HEADWORD: Pythagorism
<hw>Py*thag"o*rism</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Gr.
<?/.]</ety> <def>The doctrines taught by Pythagoras.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><note>⟦hand⟧ Pythagoras made numbers the basis of his philosophical
system, as well physical as metaphysical. The doctrine of the
transmigration of souls (metempsychosis) is associated closely with name
of Pythagoras.</note>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

